<br/><font color='#21749c' size='18' face='PuristaBold'>MISSION INTENT</font>
<br/>First, cut their communications and disable the radar and SAM sites on Skalisty Island. Once that's done, proceed to the vehicle depot, steal your getaway vehicles and reach the docks of Elektro. In the docks find the sub, attach a target beacon to it so the friendly jets can bomb it. Finally, exfil from the area.
<br/>
<br/>
<br/><font color='#21749c' size='18' face='PuristaBold'>OBJECTIVES</font>
<br/><font color='#21749c' size='16' face='PuristaSemiBold'>Skalisty Island:</font>
<br/> - Disable the radio transmitter.
<br/> - Blow up the SAM sites (2x).
<br/> - Destroy the radar station.
<br/>
<br/><font color='#21749c' size='16' face='PuristaSemiBold'>Kamyshovo:</font>
<br/> - Steal vehicles from the motorpool.
<br/>
<br/><font color='#21749c' size='16' face='PuristaSemiBold'>Elektrozavodsk:</font>
<br/> - Find the sub.
<br/> - Attach the target beacon and wait for the strike.
<br/>
<br/><font color='#21749c' size='16' face='PuristaSemiBold'>Topolka Dam:</font>
